### Create a badge definition (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/badges
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "First Steps",
  "description": "Completed your first certified module",
  "imageS3Key": "badges/first-steps.webp",
  "threshold": 1
}

###

### List all badge definitions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/badges
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update a badge
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/badges/{{badgeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "description": "Earned after completing 1 certified module"
}

###

### Get badges earned by a user (guide ownership enforced)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/badges/earned/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Delete a badge definition (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/badges/{{badgeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
